title: Total_Uninstall_Portable_6.2.3_Multilingual.paf.exe
description:
Multilingual: Arabic, Armenian, Bulgarian, SimpChinese, TradChinese, Croatian, Czech, Dutch, English, French, German, Greek, Hebrew, Hungarian, Indonesian, Italian, Japanese, Korean, Malaysian, Norwegian, Persian, Polish, Portuguese, PortugueseBR, Romanian, Russian, Serbian, Slovak, Spanish, Swedish, Turkish, Ukrainian)

Extract and run TotalUninstallPortable.
Language set by launcher according Windows localization, if you don't want: edit TotalUninstallPortable.ini with UserDefaultLang=false.
If you have Registry Workshop Portable extracted in the same location: you can use it as default registry editor in Total Uninstall, edit TotalUninstallPortable.ini with RegistryWorkshopIntegration=true.
Settings of installed TotalUninstall should be preserved.
